title: LetsBeatCOVID.net launches to track the spread of the Coronavirus in the UK/US
description: A startup behind one of the world’s most successful tech platforms for doctors has launched a new initiative to try and track the spread of the Coronavirus, initially in the UK but soon in the US. Developed by MedShr – the app used by a million doctors to aid…
